{"tid":1803057,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁振英建議要求審計署了解 有沒有空間削減港台經費","createTime":"2019-12-30T02:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T03:14:11.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4811c7dbdf311403b3034a02b78066e5c94f01ce","tid":1803057,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:28:53.000Z","msg":"全國政協副主席、前行政長官梁振英在社交網站貼文，建議政府不如要求審計署全面審查香港電台帳目，衡工量值，以今天網台林立，香港人只有750萬乘24小時的接收新聞資訊和娛樂節目為前提，了解有沒有空間削減港台經費。<br />\n<br />\n20多位香港電台節目顧問團成員，日前去信商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華，表示留意到香港電台節目製作人員工會表示，港台新聞部因報道反修例運動花費大增，超出年度預算約500萬元，因而要扣減人手，相反警隊過去半年逾時工作津貼開支共約9億5000萬元。信中指，同樣是為市民服務，港台員工待遇差天共地，要求當局為港台增撥資源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500001-20191229.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500001-20191229.htm&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkRx0icFY2nnrImD0qQ%2FuO9w%3D&h=9ec43dbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500001-20191229.htm&h=4fca07fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500001-20191229.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n可以簽聯署聲援港台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe0eZ9SHqpTj330WENMd-PGJDEcnnVNn9btktuFvrn0SG1-PA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSe0eZ9SHqpTj330WENMd-PGJDEcnnVNn9btktuFvrn0SG1-PA%2Fviewform&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkRx0icFY2nnrImD0qQ%2FuO9w%3D&h=f991bcad\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe0eZ9SHqpTj330WENMd-PGJDEcnnVNn9btktuFvrn0SG1-PA/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"c462760f773a757f4a2011c46e39264f83d5fa2b","tid":1803057,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"<i